Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//--------------------OPCN---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.16,0:00:33.97,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「いま！」という　この瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:39.40,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}なんだって　音楽に　出来たらいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:44.18,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}まだ　全力で　やり切ってない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:46.90,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}悔し涙　拭ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.43,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}青春のフレージング
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.43,0:00:55.46,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}奇跡が　努力の　先にあるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:01:01.15,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}限界は　あたしが決める
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.15,0:01:03.31,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}響け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.31,0:01:10.17,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}もう一回　大げさな夢を　探しにいこう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.17,0:01:13.78,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}止めない　勇気こそ　強さ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:20.57,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}何百回　挑戦かさねて　ここまで来た
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.57,0:01:24.97,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}チャンスの神様　みててね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.97,0:01:27.55,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}忘れたくないメロディ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.55,0:01:30.22,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}離したくないメロディ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.22,0:01:33.25,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}輝きに変えて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:38.28,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想いよ　届け…！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.16,0:00:33.97,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「此时此刻」的这个瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:39.40,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}希望能以音乐将其铭刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:44.18,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}还未拼尽全力到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:46.90,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不断拭去的悔恨泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.43,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是青春的分句
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.43,0:00:55.46,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}若是努力之后便会有奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:01:01.15,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那极限由我来决定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.15,0:01:03.31,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}吹响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.31,0:01:10.17,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}再一次去追寻那庞大的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.17,0:01:13.78,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}强大就是永不放弃的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:20.57,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}经历数百次的挑战　来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.57,0:01:24.97,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}请机会之神看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.97,0:01:27.55,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不想忘记的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.55,0:01:30.22,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不愿放开的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.22,0:01:33.25,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}变为耀眼的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:38.28,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}将这份心意　传递出去…！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,--------------------PART--------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.12,0:00:01.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.40,0:00:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.75,0:00:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明年一定要拿到金奖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.38,0:00:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我很高兴你能坚持到现在」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.42,0:00:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「非常动听的乐声」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.03,0:00:13.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.44,0:00:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.03,0:01:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三年生从社团引退
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.12,0:01:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们开始了新干部的选举
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.95,0:01:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是被指名为部长的吉川优子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.13,0:02:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位有反对意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.38,0:02:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.49,0:02:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.43,0:02:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢各位
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.88,0:02:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  新任部长就由我来担任
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.59,0:02:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是副部长的选举
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是被指名为副部长的中川夏纪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.13,0:02:21.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位有反对意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.10,0:02:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来当副部长？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.38,0:02:26.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没听说过这事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没和你说过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.18,0:02:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈们在想些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.60,0:02:32.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.70,0:02:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听到是你当部长的时候也是匪夷所思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.58,0:02:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord2.5\fsp3}你什么意思啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟这是明日香学姐希望的人选
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.38,0:02:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人完全是觉得好玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.52,0:02:44.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,综上所述
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.02,0:02:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我对这事兴趣不大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.89,0:02:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过既然是学姐拜托的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.38,0:02:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后我会好好辅佐这家伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.01,0:02:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.82,0:02:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你不要随便用手指指人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.60,0:02:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了  部长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:03:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然敢嘲弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.44,0:03:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样  北宇治高中吹奏乐部迈入了新的开端
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我的内心却有种说不出的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:15.39,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1040,720)\bord1.5\blur2\fad(500,0)}初春的终曲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:28.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,演奏很薄弱…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.74,0:03:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明年必须得努力招募新部员才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  在学校指导就是这么一回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:45.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花费一年时间所积累的东西  又会立刻回到原点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才喜欢在学校指导
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.22,0:03:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每年都从起点重新开始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.30,0:03:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这是件很棒的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.12,0:04:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.85,0:04:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是萨克斯君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.84,0:04:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又要开始转转转了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:11.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竞赛会期间我可是一直都在忍着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.01,0:04:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三年生引退了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感到寂寞了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:21.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.27,0:04:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我原以为你是不会这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.47,0:04:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得最后就这样结束真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心中充满了遗憾…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为没有拿到金奖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是秀一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:55.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  去找他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.82,0:04:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:04:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.80,0:05:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.01,0:05:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是从冢本那里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿到过什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秀一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.40,0:05:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有到处去说吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在大赛前一天  你不是送了我发夹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.56,0:05:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么可能去说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.41,0:05:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.64,0:05:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想再打进全国大赛  然后拿到金奖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还会有新的部员加入呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们打进过全国大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:51.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明年想必会有很多人加入吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:54.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…不知道我们能否好好指导他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:06:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是青春呢  两位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.27,0:06:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做伪证可是重罪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.08,0:06:11.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得秀一从小就有点那个意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.07,0:06:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过久美子怎么想我不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.53,0:06:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.69,0:06:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么关系  不用这样否认吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恋爱  还有社团
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.80,0:06:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是青春
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.50,0:06:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是认真说的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:22.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:25.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是老样子喜欢信口开河
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.50,0:06:31.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是真的很爱你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.34,0:06:32.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又开始说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.76,0:06:37.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:41.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就要走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我还有要事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:50.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是觉得好久不见  那么快就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有好久不见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.42,0:06:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才引退一个月都不到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.29,0:06:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.64,0:07:03.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和明日香之间发生了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和明日香…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.81,0:07:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事发生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.81,0:07:13.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄前同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.73,0:07:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.92,0:07:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为是明日香学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.67,0:08:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.15,0:08:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的乐声像极了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.74,0:08:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬启  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉像这样用书信来交流  有点不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.03,0:08:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时至二月  天气越渐寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.74,0:08:28.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.54,0:08:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学习马马虎虎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.18,0:08:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都在练习
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然妈妈现在开始担心我的未来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.96,0:08:42.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我还是想再去一次全国大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.30,0:08:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想拿到金奖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:47.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想留下后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像姐姐说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:56.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  有请毕业生入场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:59.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐  学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有种非常久违的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然只是几周没来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.83,0:09:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香织学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord2.5\fsp3}入戏好快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:46.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和前辈们一起度过的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.78,0:10:50.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一切对我们来说都是无可替代的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.43,0:10:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能把这份情感延续给后辈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续把北宇治吹奏乐部发扬光大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:10:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后一定要在全国大赛夺得金…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.71,0:11:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这么重要的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.03,0:11:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.52,0:11:04.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.65,0:11:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  让我们带着决心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.76,0:11:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这首歌献给各位毕业生们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.03,0:16:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  明日香学姐已经回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:08.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.92,0:16:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她倒是说过去要去一下乐器室
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,致答辞  有请毕业生代表田中明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.64,0:16:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答辞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.96,0:16:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这蕴含着春日温暖的阳光下…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.64,0:16:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师  感谢您的教导
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.76,0:17:01.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐  请多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:02.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要有大学生的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.11,0:17:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐不在了我该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.00,0:17:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会来看你们的定期演奏会的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是部长  要坚强一点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.07,0:17:24.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄前同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看见明日香学姐了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  不知道她在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.70,0:17:55.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位新入学的同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.76,0:17:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到北宇治高中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.44,0:18:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们祝贺青春闪耀的各位入学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.39,0:18:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  黄前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.97,0:18:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这里做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.62,0:18:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐你才是  在这做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.13,0:18:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太擅长应付那种场合
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你毕业
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是都说了不擅长应付吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.72,0:18:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这些  你有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.11,0:18:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有话想对明日香学姐说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.04,0:18:40.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我？你刚才是在找我？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:41.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.29,0:18:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.48,0:18:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非是关于恋爱的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.78,0:18:46.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.78,0:18:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前很不擅长和学姐你相处
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:18:57.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你是学姐  又和我是一个组
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.74,0:18:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我尽量不去这样想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.88,0:19:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我一直觉得你是个很难懂的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.36,0:19:05.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定  内心曾经是讨厌你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.90,0:19:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你想说的话？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.82,0:19:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.32,0:19:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.87,0:19:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为  这些事我都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.79,0:19:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为现在我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.12,0:19:23.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜欢学姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.32,0:19:31.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然明日香学姐你从来不表露真心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.39,0:19:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是一副高高在上的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还说什么朋友的事根本不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.70,0:19:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…但是现在我感到好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.58,0:19:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想再多听听学姐吹奏的悠风号
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.44,0:19:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想吹出明日香学姐那样的乐声
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你想说的话？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…你父亲的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经用不到它了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.97,0:20:18.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次就由黄前你吹奏这首曲子给后辈听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想说再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.15,0:20:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就不说了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.29,0:20:44.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.82,0:21:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾几何时  明日香学姐吹奏给我听的这首曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.44,0:21:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那个时候我第一次知道了它的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.46,0:21:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b0\bord0\1c&H97918F&\fs80\fsp2\frz349\pos(814,736)}吹响吧!悠风号
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.40,0:21:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.30,0:21:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.54,0:21:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中午开始合奏练习
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.61,0:21:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  这就来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.87,0:21:50.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「吹响吧!悠风号」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.00,0:21:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永远不会忘记它那温暖的乐声
